152
00:08:12,020 --> 00:08:14,000
If you don't give it to me today, don't think of leaving.

153
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:16,400
- You really can't understand.<br>- Hey!

154
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:28,800
- Boss.<br>- Where are you going?

155
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:31,000
