161
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:50,000
<i>Get in! Get in! Behave!</i>

162
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:52,600
<i>You two better behave! Do you hear me?</i>

163
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:56,300
You dead fatty who has no conscience! Dirty thing! Stinky evil person!

164
00:08:56,300 --> 00:08:58,400
