200
00:11:20,270 --> 00:11:21,580
None.

201
00:11:21,580 --> 00:11:22,880
Here.

202
00:11:24,160 --> 00:11:26,350
Buddy, are you a foreigner?

203
00:11:26,380 --> 00:11:27,810
What?

204
00:11:27,810 --> 00:11:29,580
