205
00:11:29,590 --> 00:11:30,640
What treasure?

206
00:11:30,640 --> 00:11:32,200
Blue-and-white porcelain.

207
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:33,240
Blue-and-white porcelain?

208
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:35,280
