211
00:11:41,060 --> 00:11:44,120
If not because I need money right away, I won't be rushing to sell this.

212
00:11:52,600 --> 00:11:54,770
There was even such a kind of treasure on this small island.

213
00:11:54,770 --> 00:11:56,400
If this is in the capital,

214
00:11:56,400 --> 00:11:58,160
