375
00:22:20,660 --> 00:22:22,720
I told you before.

376
00:22:22,720 --> 00:22:27,230
I am a businessman. Yes.

377
00:22:27,230 --> 00:22:29,010
You gave me that money.

378
00:22:29,010 --> 00:22:33,820
