384
00:22:49,230 --> 00:22:50,550
Not much.

385
00:22:51,690 --> 00:22:52,850
5,000 liang.

386
00:22:52,850 --> 00:22:56,070
Why don't you just go steal?

387
00:22:56,070 --> 00:22:58,010
I am a businessman.

