Oh, right.

391
00:23:03,900 --> 00:23:06,970
I still have to watch the game later.

392
00:23:06,970 --> 00:23:11,300
Jeez, this competition is quite exciting.

393
00:23:11,300 --> 00:23:13,570
Oh, right.

394
00:23:13,570 --> 00:23:16,900
I am exactly going to watch how those two friends of yours

395
00:23:16,900 --> 00:23:18,690
