399
00:23:25,040 --> 00:23:28,830
- Move!<br>- If you want to make a bet, I will welcome it.

400
00:23:28,830 --> 00:23:32,070
If you want to cause trouble, no way! Throw him out!

401
00:23:32,070 --> 00:23:34,720
- Yes! Move!<br>- You dead fatty!

402
00:23:34,720 --> 00:23:37,700
You dishonest dead fatty!

403
00:23:38,520 --> 00:23:39,850
Hurry and leave! Hurry and leave!

404
00:23:39,850 --> 00:23:42,090
