411
00:24:03,710 --> 00:24:06,810
I disdain having dealings with them.

412
00:24:06,810 --> 00:24:08,730
- Hey!<br>- Yes.

413
00:24:08,730 --> 00:24:10,910
Can you help me?

414
00:24:10,910 --> 00:24:12,260
What?

415
00:24:12,260 --> 00:24:14,460
Do you want me to help them fight?

416
00:24:14,460 --> 00:24:16,570
I don't mean it that way.

417
00:24:16,570 --> 00:24:18,080
If you can help my friends,

