420
00:24:25,330 --> 00:24:26,650
Don't forget.

421
00:24:26,650 --> 00:24:28,950
It was you who stole my item.

422
00:24:28,950 --> 00:24:30,310
I not only didn't kill you,

423
00:24:30,310 --> 00:24:32,520
