474
00:27:32,700 --> 00:27:34,740
Go and open the doors.

475
00:27:36,560 --> 00:27:38,890
Hurry. This way.

476
00:27:40,670 --> 00:27:44,460
Older Bro Fei, Older Bro Fei, my 'fierce tiger going down the mountain' won't work this time.

477
00:27:44,460 --> 00:27:47,990
