600
00:38:03,640 --> 00:38:05,640
Zhan Xiong Fei!

601
00:38:09,800 --> 00:38:11,450
Zhan Xiong Fei!

602
00:38:15,000 --> 00:38:16,370
Zhan Xiong Fei!

603
00:38:16,370 --> 00:38:19,410
